<h2>About Me</h2>

My username is Destroyere1107. I'm a massive nerd, and that's really it. You
might be expecting a long and heartfelt story about my life and how I came to be
the person I am today. <br />That would take effort on my part.
<br />Regardless, there isn't really that much stuff to say about me. <br />I'm
Coloradan, I fix computers, I 3D print, I like calculators. <br />I'm also a bit
of a Linux purist. I've been using Linux for a while now. It's bad. <br />I am
fully unable to use Windows now because of how unintutive and bloated it is
compared to any Linux distro, even Ubuntu. <br />I run Fedora and downstream
friends on basically everything now. <br />Also, KDE. Please donate to KDE.
<br />In the future, I will ask you here to sign a guestbook. It's coming
Eventually™. <br />If you stick around, you'll be seeing a lot of Eventually™
and Coming Soon™. <br />Just like this page. More about me, Coming Soon™.
<br /><br />Important Note: I may not be a part of the LGBTQ+ community, but I
stand <b>firmly as an ally</b>.

